item.title: CVE-2022-3209|2024-08-03T01:00:10.808Z -- unknown -- soledad
item.description: The soledad WordPress theme before 8.2.5 does not sanitise the {id,datafilter[type],...} parameters in its penci_more_slist_post_ajax AJAX action, leading to a Reflected Cross-Site Scripting (XSS) vulnerability.
